Package spoon.metamodel

Ready to go meta? This package contains classes that model the Spoon metamodel itself.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Metamodel
    Represents the Spoon metamodel (incl.
    MetamodelConcept
    Represents a concept of the Spoon metamodel (eg CtClass).
    MetamodelProperty
    Represents a property of the Spoon metamodel.
    MMMethod
    Represents a method used to get or set a MetamodelProperty of a MetamodelConcept.

Package spoon.metamodel Description

Ready to go meta? This package contains classes that model the Spoon metamodel itself. So this is the metametamodel.
